type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

!! Project status report

Multi-tiddler context: the `tagged-children` template collects all tiddlers tagged with the current tiddler (treating it as a project). The status report is created as a new child tiddler.

''Settings covered:'' action mode, multi-tiddler context (by tag), `output-mode: text`, `output-target: new-tiddler`, `output-title-template` with date, prompt template precedence

!!! Setup

# Create a project tiddler (e.g. "My Project")
# Tag task tiddlers with the project name
# Optionally add a `status` field to each task (e.g. `done`, `in-progress`, `blocked`)

```
<$button>
  Generate status report
  <$llm-action
    tiddler=<<currentTiddler>>
    promptTemplate="$:/plugins/rimir/llm-connect/prompts/status-report"
  />
</$button>
```

